benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: POST /1.0/kb/accounts/{accountId}/tags - Add tags to account

covered: POST Valid Payload: Comprehensive coverage for valid payloads with 201 responses and Tag objects (TC01, TC02, TC03, TC04, TC05, TC18, TC24).
POST Large Payloads and Deduplication: Large payload test (TC18) and deduplication in request (TC19) are covered.
POST Invalid Payload: Empty body, non-array body, and extra fields are rejected (TC07, TC08, TC17).
POST Validation: Invalid tag definition IDs and formats (TC09, TC10, TC13, TC23).
POST Authorization: Missing/invalid authentication and missing header scenarios (TC11, TC15).
POST Server Error Handling: Service unavailability returns 503 (TC16).
POST Query Parameters Handling: Pagination/Sorting/Filtering parameters in POST are ignored (TC06).
POST Duplicate Submission: Duplicates in the request are handled gracefully (TC19).
Edge-case Security: Header injection content sanitized (TC22).
gaps: Rate Limiting: No tests for rate limiting or throttling of POST requests.
Caching Behavior: No tests for caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control).
Authorization: No tests for insufficient permissions (403) scenario; Only tests for missing header (400) and missing/invalid token (401).
Internal Server Error path: No explicit 500 Internal Server Error test; only 503.
recommendations: Add rate-limiting tests to verify throttling and fairness behavior under load.
Add tests for caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control).
Add tests for 403 Forbidden when permissions are insufficient to add tags.
Add tests for 500 Internal Server Error path to simulate DB failures.
Extend tests to verify content-type and Accept header handling for incorrect values.
